     About Us
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
     Forest Lawn Memorial Park is dedicated to providing a serene and respectful environment for the final resting places of your loved ones. Our beautifully maintained grounds and comprehensive services ensure that every visit is a peaceful and meaningful experience.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center mt-8">
     <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
      <img alt="Forest Lawn Memorial Park entrance with lush greenery" class="rounded-lg" height="250" src="images/vismis.jpg"/>
     </div>
     <div class="md:w-1/2 mt-8 md:mt-0">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">
       Mission
      </h3>
      <p>
       The Forest Lawn Memorial Park is committed to promoting general acceptance to the concepts of memorialization and pre-need planning. It is committed to support community building through partnership with the local community in the furtherance of higher level of education, spiritual, environment, economic and aesthetic values.
    </p>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 mt-8">
     Vision
    </h3>
    <p>
     An Organization that is committed to provide the residents of Rodriguez (formerly Montalban) San Mateo, Marikina, Quezon City and its nearby key localities the cleanest and the most modern memorial park. At the same time, to provide the best quality of service in partnership with its sales agents, clientele and determination to completely develop a memorial park.
    </p>
   </div>
  </div>
 </div>
